<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Inventory API Report</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 36px;
      color: #222;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    h1, h2 {
      color: #7a3b1d;
    }
    .note {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: #fff3e8;
      border-left: 5px solid #c56b2d;
      margin: 18px 0 28px 0;
    }
    .section {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    th {
      background: #f7f7f7;
    }
    code {
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
      background: #f3f3f3;
      padding: 2px 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Bao Cao Chuc Nang Inventory API</h1>
  <p>Du an: <b>NNPTUD-BT6</b></p>
  <p>Noi dung bao gom ma nguon Inventory, cac file Postman import duoc, va tai lieu minh hoa cac chuc nang can test.</p>

  <div class="note">
    <b>Luu y:</b> Moi truong CLI nay khong mo duoc Postman GUI de chup man hinh thuc te.
    Tai lieu nay da chuan bi san bo cuc Word-compatible va cac anh minh hoa cho tung API.
    Neu giang vien yeu cau dung anh chup Postman that, hay mo cac file JSON trong thu muc <code>post/</code>, run request trong Postman, sau do thay cac anh minh hoa bang screenshot thuc te.
  </div>

  <h2>1. Danh sach API da lam</h2>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Chuc nang</th>
      <th>Method</th>
      <th>Endpoint</th>
    </tr>
    <tr><td>Tao product va tu dong tao inventory</td><td>POST</td><td>/api/v1/products</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Lay danh sach inventory co join product</td><td>GET</td><td>/api/v1/inventories</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Lay inventory theo ID co join product</td><td>GET</td><td>/api/v1/inventories/:id</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Tang stock</td><td>POST</td><td>/api/v1/inventories/add-stock</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Giam stock</td><td>POST</td><td>/api/v1/inventories/remove-stock</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Reservation</td><td>POST</td><td>/api/v1/inventories/reservation</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Sold</td><td>POST</td><td>/api/v1/inventories/sold</td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>2. Minh hoa tao product va tu dong tao inventory</h2>
    <p>Import file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code> vao Postman, mo request <code>Create Product - Auto Create Inventory</code>, dien <code>categoryId</code> hop le va send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/01-create-product.svg" alt="Create product" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>3. Minh hoa get all inventories</h2>
    <p>Trong file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code>, mo request <code>Get All Inventories</code> va send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/02-get-all-inventories.svg" alt="Get all inventories" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>4. Minh hoa get inventory by ID</h2>
    <p>Trong file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code>, mo request <code>Get Inventory By ID</code>, dien <code>inventoryId</code> thuc te, sau do send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/03-get-inventory-by-id.svg" alt="Get inventory by id" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>5. Minh hoa add stock</h2>
    <p>Trong file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code>, mo request <code>Add Stock</code>, dien <code>productId</code> va send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/04-add-stock.svg" alt="Add stock" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>6. Minh hoa remove stock</h2>
    <p>Trong file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code>, mo request <code>Remove Stock</code>, dien <code>productId</code> va send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/05-remove-stock.svg" alt="Remove stock" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>7. Minh hoa reservation</h2>
    <p>Trong file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code>, mo request <code>Reservation</code>, dien <code>productId</code> va send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/06-reservation.svg" alt="Reservation" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>8. Minh hoa sold</h2>
    <p>Trong file <code>post/inventory-today.postman_collection.json</code>, mo request <code>Sold</code>, dien <code>productId</code> va send request.</p>
    <img src="assets/07-sold.svg" alt="Sold" />
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>9. Thu tu test de nhin ro bien dong du lieu</h2>
    <p>1) Tao product, 2) add stock, 3) reservation, 4) sold, 5) get inventory by ID.</p>
    <p>Du lieu ky vong: <code>stock</code> giam dan, <code>reserved</code> tang roi giam, <code>soldCount</code> tang sau khi goi API sold.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
